     <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start"><div class="max-w-3xl flex-1"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent mb-4">July 10, 2026</p><h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-zinc-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">How to Get an ADHD Disability Doctor's Note</h1><p class="mt-6 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">A well-written doctor's note is often the cornerstone of any ADHD disability claim -- whether for workplace accommodations, school services, or SSDI benefits. Here is how to get one that actually helps.</p></div><div class="hidden md:block w-80 flex-shrink-0"><img src="/images/blog-doctor-note.webp" alt="Medical professional providing documentation for ADHD disability claim" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full" width="320" height="213" loading="eager" /></div></div>
